gg_dio_stoned

___________________________________
This is my first map ever. I made it for our GG server. 
This is a dark map and has 32 spawn points.

This map contains 2 spawn sections on opposite ends of the main fighting area which is lowly lit. It also has 2 halls going down each side which are even less lit. 

There is a tall platform in the middle that overlooks most of the map.

This map should provide lots of knifing opportunities.

I was going for gameplay and quick games instead of "purdyness".....
perhaps the next one will have more eye candy
